        <abstract> 
<p>Pleased that JC-B will review <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Fears he will not be able to improve the book with JC-B’s "wonderfully curious" photographs because Murray printed such a large edition.</p>
            <p>Would be glad to have JC-B’s notes on inheritance – "a most important subject".</p>
